{
  "stem": "16503.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 358.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now that was when I was helping the two transports.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This is what I saw.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So when we were called up, I was pretty much ready for what was coming in that sense, only I wasn't ready for the doors to be shut on me with people just standing and being completely squeezed in an absolute position of-- you could sit, but you didn't have much room.",
      "word_count": 52
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "People were-- there are claustrophobic people in, in decent circumstances.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it was screaming and yelling and screaming and yelling.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I think my family was extremely disciplined.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We stayed together in a corner like, and we sat down on the floor.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And that was it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And when they closed the door it was very scary because it was dark.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was absolutely dark.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I think there must have been a little slit at the top of the wagon.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I'm not sure.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Anyhow, this finally started to move.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You heard the screaming and hollering in the-- on the outside until everything was loaded.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the last door shut and, and, and sealed, and then we went.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And how long?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I know it went up and it went like backwards and forwards, but how long we were there would be very hard for me to even guess.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Did you stop along the way?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We stopped.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We Going backwards.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We stopped.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We move forwards.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "On-- in no way was the wagon open-- at no time.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So we didn't have water.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We had the bucket there, and we were sitting down in the nowhere land, as I call it.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] That would be about my description.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I got a marvelous mechanism in my body, and I think are lots of people have learned it too.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You kind of disconnect.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
